{"tid":1316913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小編就說過，警民衝突真的可以很醜陋。","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T19:41:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46512ae8ced9487211837078a7af586b54f84ef6","tid":1316913,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:00:22.000Z","msg":".<br />\n你想想你們警察還有多少張牌？真槍？水炮車？但現在示威者那邊只是剛起步，會揮下拳動，連正式暴動的DIY武器都未出現，而且他們更傾向穿少防具，沒有策略性圍剿。另外，所謂的人肉搜尋除了公開已公開資訊，都沒有後續性騷擾。<br />\n.<br />\n用比較多人熟悉的六七暴動做例子，現在連那級數都未到，你們就弄得如此狼狽，還可以笑住人齊收隊多少次？不要以為自己那幾套破衣服與頭盔真是銅皮鐵骨，便胡亂來都沒人傷到你們。<br />\n..<br />\n所以小編勸你們做回真正的警察。那些是職責範圍市民很了解，但那些超出了範圍，例如濫用武力、打記者、選擇性執法、不出示證件...就不要再做了。其實香港市民要求從來不多。<br />\n.<br />\n當然你們下次可升級開槍，讓仇恨旋渦一直往上捲，然後雙方死傷數以百計，再有無數的游擊戰與尋仇。歷史不是沒有上演過，甚至南美中東非洲現正上映中，小編可以說得那麼篤定因為看過太多。<br />\n.<br />\n但何苦讓社會淪落如此？當只要你們公正辦事就可以避免一切時。<br />\n.<br />\n你們責任是維持社會和諧，但和諧不是「死人才不會出聲」那種，你們看太多古龍小說了。你們沒必要成為社會仇恨的燃油，政治事就由政治官出來解決吧。"},{"pid":"e21b61ac768e5f050d6ee9a21ffa206276a6f0d2","tid":1316913,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:03:01.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">你扮警察\n有人冒警\n我冇嘢講\n我要搵律師</code></pre>"},{"pid":"11574ac894a1b55d173482e1f2b7dee4f23afcf6","tid":1316913,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/263626817164631/posts/1120060141521290?s=100002126184316&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F263626817164631%2Fposts%2F1120060141521290%3Fs%3D100002126184316%26sfns%3Dmo&d=LzMeHrLekQtOmJ7gjClTQBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b1f15d0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/263626817164631/posts/1120060141521290?s=100002126184316&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"fb75fa1c68cb99f683e075a5c2ea470995d47801","tid":1316913,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c43f64adee74254c3a08aa7bdb6d7caa8c6b11b","tid":1316913,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab43663e9958225c91c402bd1eb8d2e0c235759","tid":1316913,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:41:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5870bcc834ec5b527c12e8e68c2613ea280cc507","tid":1316913,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c43f64adee74254c3a08aa7bdb6d7caa8c6b11b","tid":1316913,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"你就係恐懼鳥？我當年係城大唔知你有上高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"aa2464cc86b86a901d9733242d7ce60f6f017599","tid":1316913,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:43:52.000Z","msg":"夠膽就出"},{"pid":"555e4009f1fb088c3428829ffe20d61dbacdadfb","tid":1316913,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5870bcc834ec5b527c12e8e68c2613ea280cc507","tid":1316913,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c43f64adee74254c3a08aa7bdb6d7caa8c6b11b","tid":1316913,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"你就係恐懼鳥？我當年係城大唔知你有上高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:45:00.000Z","msg":"唔係，轉貼咋"},{"pid":"059d86ee5cb15d5c5a3be3df6f2f3efc7f9c4228","tid":1316913,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e